<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>RE7LA - Rapport Statistique Officiel</title>
    <style>
        @page { margin: 40px; }
        body { font-family: 'Helvetica', sans-serif; color: #1e293b; line-height: 1.5; }
        
        /* Header Branding */
        .pdf-header { display: table; width: 100%; border-bottom: 2px solid #f1f5f9; padding-bottom: 20px; margin-bottom: 30px; }
        .header-logo { display: table-cell; width: 50%; vertical-align: middle; }
        .header-info { display: table-cell; width: 50%; text-align: right; vertical-align: middle; }
        .logo-text { font-size: 26px; font-weight: 900; color: #2C3E50; }
        .logo-text span { color: #F7B731; }
        .doc-type { font-size: 10px; font-weight: 700; color: #94a3b8; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 2px; }

        .row { display: table; width: 100%; margin-bottom: 25px; table-layout: fixed; }
        .col { display: table-cell; vertical-align: top; padding: 10px; }
        .card { border: 1px solid #f1f5f9; border-radius: 16px; padding: 20px; background: #fff; box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.02); }
        
        /* KPI Grid */
        .kpi-row { display: table; width: 100%; margin-bottom: 30px; border-spacing: 10px; }
        .kpi-box { display: table-cell; text-align: center; padding: 20px; background: #f8fafc; border: 1px solid #e2e8f0; border-radius: 16px; }
        .kpi-val { font-size: 24px; font-weight: 900; color: #2C3E50; }
        .kpi-label { font-size: 10px; color: #64748b; text-transform: uppercase; font-weight: 700; margin-top: 5px; letter-spacing: 1px; }
        
        h3 { font-size: 14px; color: #334155; border-bottom: 2px solid #f1f5f9; padding-bottom: 10px; margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 15px; font-weight: 800; text-transform: uppercase; }
        .chart-img { max-width: 100%; border-radius: 12px; }
        
        table { width: 100%; border-collapse: separate; border-spacing: 0; font-size: 11px; }
        table th, table td { padding: 12px; text-align: left; border-bottom: 1px solid #f1f5f9; }
        table th { background: #f8fafc; color: #64748b; font-weight: 700; text-transform: uppercase; font-size: 9px; }
        
        /* Footer & Stamps */
        .official-footer { display: table; width: 100%; margin-top: 50px; border-top: 1px solid #f1f5f9; padding-top: 30px; }
        .signature-block { display: table-cell; width: 60%; vertical-align: bottom; }
        .stamp-block { display: table-cell; width: 40%; text-align: center; vertical-align: middle; }
        
        .stamp { width: 110px; height: 110px; border: 3px double #e11d48; border-radius: 50%; display: inline-block; position: relative; transform: rotate(-10deg); opacity: 0.7; }
        .stamp-inner { position: absolute; top: 50%; left: 50%; transform: translate(-50%, -50%); color: #e11d48; font-weight: 900; font-size: 9px; text-align: center; line-height: 1.2; }
        
        .signature { border-bottom: 1px solid #2C3E50; width: 180px; padding-bottom: 5px; margin-top: 25px; font-family: 'Cursive', serif; font-size: 18px; color: #2C3E50; }
        .footer-note { font-size: 9px; color: #94a3b8; text-align: center; margin-top: 40px; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="pdf-header">
    <div class="header-logo">
        <div class="logo-text">RE7<span>LA</span></div>
        <div style="font-size: 10px; color: #64748b; font-weight: 600;">Data Intelligence Unit</div>
    </div>
    <div class="header-info">
        <div class="doc-type">Rapport d'Analyse Performance</div>
        <div style="font-size: 12px; color: #1e293b; font-weight: 700; margin-top: 5px;">Période: {{ "now"|date('F Y') }}</div>
        <div style="font-size: 11px; color: #94a3b8;">Généré le {{ "now"|date('d/m/Y') }}</div>
    </div>
</div>

<div class="kpi-row">
    <div class="kpi-box">
        <div class="kpi-val">{{ totalPromos }}</div>
        <div class="kpi-label">Catalogue</div>
    </div>
    <div class="kpi-box">
        <div class="kpi-val">{{ totalReservations }}</div>
        <div class="kpi-label">Ventes</div>
    </div>
    <div class="kpi-box">
        <div class="kpi-val">{{ totalViews }}</div>
        <div class="kpi-label">Visibilité</div>
    </div>
    <div class="kpi-box">
        <div class="kpi-val">{{ engagementRate }}%</div>
        <div class="kpi-label">Engagement</div>
    </div>
</div>

<div class="row">
    <div class="col">
        <div class="card">
            <h3>Distribution des Offres</h3>
            <div style="text-align: center;">
                <img src="{{ pieChartUrl }}" class="chart-img">
            </div>
            <div style="font-size:10px; color:#64748b; margin-top:10px; text-align: center;">
                Individuelles: <strong>{{ nbIndiv }}</strong> | Packs: <strong>{{ nbPacks }}</strong>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col">
        <div class="card">
            <h3>Répartition Catégories</h3>
            <div style="text-align: center;">
                <img src="{{ doughnutChartUrl }}" class="chart-img">
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<div class="row">
    <div class="col" style="width: 100%;">
        <div class="card">
            <h3>Performance du Top 10 (Réservations)</h3>
            <div style="text-align: center;">
                <img src="{{ barChartUrl }}" class="chart-img" style="width: 100%;">
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<div class="row">
    <div class="col">
        <div class="card">
            <h3>💎 Clients Ambassadeurs</h3>
            <table>
                <thead>
                    <tr><th>E-mail Utilisateur</th><th style="text-align:right;">Actions</th></tr>
                </thead>
                <tbody>
                    {% for email, count in topUsers %}
                    <tr><td>{{ email }}</td><td style="text-align:right;"><strong>{{ count }}</strong></td></tr>
                    {% endfor %}
                </tbody>
            </table>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col">
        <div class="card" style="background: #f8fafc;">
            <h3>🔍 Note de Synthèse</h3>
            <p style="font-size:11px; line-height:1.7; color: #475569;">
                L'analyse des données montre un taux d'engagement de <strong>{{ engagementRate }}%</strong>. 
                Les offres groupées (Packs) représentent <strong>{{ (nbPacks / (totalPromos > 0 ? totalPromos : 1) * 100)|round }}%</strong> du volume promotionnel global. 
                <br><br>
                <strong>Recommandation :</strong> Intensifier les campagnes sur les segments à faible visibilité pour équilibrer la performance du catalogue.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<div class="official-footer">
    <div class="signature-block">
        <div style="font-size: 11px; font-weight: 800; color: #1e293b; margin-bottom: 30px;">DÉPARTEMENT ANALYTIQUE</div>
        <div class="signature">Analyst Team RE7LA</div>
        <div style="font-size: 10px; color: #94a3b8; margin-top: 5px;">Validation des Données</div>
    </div>
    <div class="stamp-block">
        <div class="stamp">
            <div class="stamp-inner">
                RAPPORT CERTIFIÉ<br>
                RE7LA TUNISIA<br>
                {{ "now"|date("Y") }}
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<div class="footer-note">
    Document confidentiel destiné à l'usage interne de RE7LA.<br>
    www.re7la.tn | Tunis, Tunisie
</div>

</body>
</html>
